      <title>这种令人讨厌的蜱传疾病曾被称为楠塔基特热，目前正呈上升趋势</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/06/10/nx-s1-4992276/once-called-nantucket-fever-this-nasty-tick-borne-illness-is-on-the-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这种蜱传疾病曾被称为楠塔基特热，目前正从东北部蔓延至中西部。一项临床试验将于本月开始，以观察一种抗疟疾药物是否能治疗这种疾病。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/06/10/nx-s1-4992276/once-called-nantucket-fever-this-nasty-tick-borne-illness-is-on-the-rise</guid>
